1.onResume   --------------------------------------------------- Home 按键坑
2.onWindowFocusChanged  ------------------------------- 锁屏开屏坑
3.OnSystemUiVisibilityChangeListener ----------------- 虚拟键盘坑
4.onConfigurationChanged -------------------------------- 虚拟键盘加旋转屏幕坑

